<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Event Dress Code</title>
    <style>
        /* Global Reset */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background: #212121;
            color: #f5f5f5;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 0 20px;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Header Section */
        header {
            position: relative;
            background: url('https://cdn.luxe.digital/media/2019/09/12085336/smart-casual-dress-code-men-style-luxury-luxe-digital.jpg') center center no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 0 20px;
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        header .cta-button {
            background-color: #f5a623;
            padding: 18px 60px;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-radius: 50px;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        header .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #ff7f00;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        /* Section Styling */
        .section {
            padding: 80px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .section h2 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #f5a623;
        }

        .section p {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            background-color: #ff6b6b;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(255, 107, 107, 0.3);
            transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #ff4b4b;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        /* Image Styling */
        .section img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 550px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        /* Footer Section */
        footer {
            background: #333333;
            color: #f5f5f5;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }

        footer p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 {
                font-size: 3.5rem;
            }

            header p {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }

            .section h2 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }

            .section img {
                max-width: 100%;
            }

            .section-content {
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header>
        <div>
            <h1>Exclusive A2_Event Dress Code</h1>
            <p>Join us in making this event unforgettable by following the dress code guidelines.</p>
            <a href="#dress-code" class="cta-button">View Dress Code</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Section 1: For Men -->
    <section class="section" id="dress-code">
        <h2>For Men: Formal Attire</h2>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>We encourage men to wear suits or tuxedos. Please pair your attire with polished shoes and accessories that complement the formal nature of the event.</p>
            
        </div>
        <br>
        <img src="https://asset20.ckassets.com/thegoodlookbook/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2019/01/How-To-Look-Hot-In-A-Kurta-Pyjama-This-Wedding-Season-e1546688910615.jpg" alt="Formal Attire for Men">
    </section>

    <!-- Section 2: For Women -->
    <section class="section">
        <h2>For Women: Elegant Evening Wear</h2>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>Women are encouraged to wear long evening gowns or sophisticated cocktail dresses. Consider luxurious fabrics such as satin or velvet for a more refined look.</p>
            
        </div>
        <br>
        <img src="https://i.etsystatic.com/25485384/r/il/b662a3/3366722538/il_570xN.3366722538_44cm.jpg" alt="Elegant Evening Wear for Women">
    </section>

    <!-- Section 3: General Guidelines -->
    <section class="section">
        <h2>General Guidelines</h2>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>Attendees should avoid casual or athletic wear, including jeans, t-shirts, sneakers, or flip-flops. We aim to maintain an upscale and elegant atmosphere.</p>
            
        </div>
        <br>
        <img src="<a href="https://ibb.co/17ZNznR"><img src="https://i.ibb.co/CmByPtV/Whats-App-Image-2024-12-05-at-23-33-30-5dfea1ad.jpg" alt="Whats-App-Image-2024-12-05-at-23-33-30-5dfea1ad" border="0">
    </section>

    <!-- Footer Section -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Exclusive Event. All rights reserved. For any questions, feel free to contact us at A2_event.com</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
